title: Here's How Much More The Top-Paid TV Actresses Make Than The Characters They Play

meta_data.description: The 15 highest-paid TV actresses made $208.5 million in the 12 months to June, while their on-screen characters would have made about $2.2 million.
meta_data.author: Madeline Berg
